Bonenburg geochemical dataset long format

bonenburg_long.Rd

This is the same dataset but now the continuous variables (e.g. measurements) are crossed with the variable Height.

bonenburg_long

Format

A data frame with 486 rows and 11 variables:

section

Name of the section

strat

First order stratigraphic units

strat2

Second order stratigraphic units

sampleid

Assigned IDs

height

Height in units cm

measurement

Type of measurement

value

Value of measurment

Source

https://www.schweizerbart.de/papers/nos/detail/52/90527/A_comparative_study_of_total_organic_carbon_d13C_signatures_in_the_Triassic_Jurassic_transitional_beds_of_the_Central_European_Basin_and_western_Tethys_shelf_seas
